{
  "title": "Istikharah Prayer",
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "section_title",
      "text": "Seeking Allah’s Guidance"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When one considers doing anything which is Islamically permissible yet he is uncertain about its benefit, he should seek the assistance of Allah (subúanahu wa ta‘ala), completely trusting in His choice."
    },
    {
      "type": "section_title",
      "text": "The Prophet’s Teaching"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Prophet (ﷺ) used to teach his companions the istikharah for all matters great or small. It is narrated by al-Bukhari as follows:",
